<p>I'm currently uploading a CSV file with values during the APEX data load wizard into below table. The trigger runs before each update on Table1 but struggling to display the htp output to the user. Anyone know how to do this in APEX?</p>  <h2>Table 1 (CSV)</h2>  <p><strong>Mobile</strong>,<strong>Address</strong>,<strong>Product</strong>,<strong>comments</strong></p>  <p>12312131,50 long street,Product1,null</p>  <p>1231231,14 blah place,Product2,comment4</p>  <h2>Trigger</h2>  <pre><code>create or replace trigger "TABLE1_T1" BEFORE  update on "TABLE1"  for each row   begin      if :old.comments is not null then      htp.prn ('Warning: ' || :new.comments || ' will replace ' ||          :old.comments);     end if;   end; </code></pre>